### 1. Successful Login
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "amara.o@example.com",
  "password": "password"
}

### 2. Login - Wrong Password (Should return 401 Unauthorized)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "amara.o@example.com",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

### 3. Login - Unregistered User (Should return 401 Unauthorized)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nobody@gmail.com",
  "password": "123"
}